性比较小，当然学历样貌也在标准内。反面他可能真的没那么在乎我，吵架永远自己的情绪比我重要。相比而言感觉他在找一个符合他标准的结婚对象，所以他喜欢我的温柔体贴聪明懂事，却不能接受我对未来生活要求的不确定性以及情绪上的不稳定。 3.关于他父母，可能由于我前期父母反对他并未对我造成影响，所以他父母的意见对他造成影响后，我过于气愤觉得父母不应该干涉，尤其在我提出退婚后他父母也无动于衷完全没有劝和意思，让我觉得他父母态度很有问题，但现在冷静下来问题还在我们自己身上，并不应该迁怒他父母。 综上，目前还在各自冷静中，如果本周他还坚持分，我可能真的要逼自己放下了。"},"attached_info":"CkAIn4za7bz1nIobEAMaCDcxODIwMDU0ING9r4sGMKQBOPEUQB1yCTQ5MjkyNDAyOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"44 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-252545c2c7b4f41c22bf16e84c02dbc8_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"30_1635212966.861668","card_id":"Q_493612511","target":{"id":493612511,"title":"为什么苹果会上架高价抛光布？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/493612511","type":"question","created":1634773858,"answer_count":163,"follower_count":306,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[18,25,32,520,4574],"comment_count":22,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8In4za7bz1nIobEAMaCDcxOTcyODk0IOLWwosGMBY4sgJAHnIJNDkzNjEyNTExeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"38 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-4f6407abf894c73f32d2583020280aad_720w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"31_1635212966.8620913","card_id":"Q_493494356","target":{"id":493494356,"title":"为什么总有玩家怀念S8的IG？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/493494356","type":"question","created":1634713392,"answer_count":234,"follower_count":470,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[18427,66379,168032],"comment_count":17,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8In4za7bz1nIobEAMaCDcxOTQ2NjU1ILD+vosGMBE41gNAH3IJNDkzNDk0MzU2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"32 